OL,3,CMum who took child in pushchair to
OL,4,Criot spared jail
OL,6,FA "naive" young mother who took her
OL,7,Fchild in a pushchair to a riot outside
OL,8,Fan asylum seeker hotel has been handed
OL,9,Fa community order.
OL,11,FNevey Smith, 21, of West Street,
OL,12,FOldham, pleaded guilty to violent
OL,13,Fdisorder after she was spotted in
OL,14,Fhelicopter footage throwing liquid
OL,15,Ffrom a bottle towards police officers.
OL,17,FThe officers were trying to maintain
OL,18,Forder outside a hotel housing asylum
OL,19,Fseekers in Newton Heath, Manchester,
OL,20,Fon 31 July, just days after the
OL,21,FSouthport stabbings.
