OL,3,CMum who took child in pushchair to
OL,4,Criot spared jail
OL,6,FJudge Patrick Field KC described
OL,7,FSmith's actions as "disturbing" during
OL,8,Fsentencing at Manchester Crown Court
OL,9,Fon 23 September.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's a disturbing feature
OL,12,Fthat you chose to join it (the riot)
OL,13,Fwith you child with you. It's a
OL,14,Fdisturbing part of this case. What
OL,15,Fwere you thinking?"
OL,17,FThe judge also told Smith that she had
OL,18,Fa "lot to learn" and "quite a lot of
OL,19,Fgrowing up to do", labelling her
OL,20,F"misguided, naive and immature".
