OL,3,CMum who took child in pushchair to
OL,4,Criot spared jail
OL,6,FSmith was handed a community order and
OL,7,Fmade to attend reviews at a women's
OL,8,Fproblem-solving court, and carry out
OL,9,F100 hours of unpaid work.
OL,11,FHer mother, Vanessa Smith, 42, was
OL,12,Falso at the protest and admitted
OL,13,Fviolent disorder and will be sentenced
OL,14,Fon Thursday, 26 September.
OL,16,FSmith is one of hundreds charged over
OL,17,Funrest that broke out after three
OL,18,Fgirls were stabbed in Southport,
OL,19,Fallegedly fuelled by false information
OL,20,Fspread about the alleged killer online.
